uiEntry.title: button_exit
uiEntry.script:
dofile "data/ui/templates/template.fe_button_standard.lua"
function OnLeaveDepress() local parent = Component.GetProperty("ParentPopup") Component.Call("Root.LuaCall", "ClosePopup", parent) end
function SetParentPopupAddress(addr) print("Setting parent address: "..tostring(addr)) Component.SetProperty("ParentPopup", addr) end

uiEntry.title: button_all
uiEntry.tooltip: When this is selected any messages you send will be sent to all players.||To only send to the players on your team switch to the team button.
uiEntry.script:
dofile "data/ui/templates/template.fe_button_standard.lua"
local this = UIComponent(Address)
function OnClickUp() UIComponent(this:Parent()):LuaCall("Notify", Component.Messages.StateChange, this:CurrentState(), Address) end
